'''Tranqarest''' was a powerful sedative.

According to [[Jedi healer/Legends|Jedi healer]] [[Tekli]], Tranqarest was so potent that it was capable of keeping even a [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] sedated, as was the case when it was used on [[Raynar Thul]].<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Star by Star">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>

